            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>
            showexponent
          </summary>
          <div style="margin-left: 22px">
            <dl>
              <dt>Parent:</dt>
              <dd>data[type=mesh3d].colorbar</dd>
              <dt>Type:</dt>
