            </dl>
            <p>
              Represents the level that incident rays are reflected in a single direction, causing shine.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>
            vertexnormalsepsilon
          </summary>
          <div style="margin-left: 22px">
            <dl>
              <dt>Parent:</dt>
