            Sets the coordinates via location IDs or names. Coordinates correspond to the centroid of each location given. See `locationmode` for more info.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>
          lon
        </summary>
        <div style="margin-left: 22px">
          <dl>
            <dt>Parent:</dt>
            <dd>data[type=scattergeo]</dd>
            <dt>Type:</dt>
            <dd>data array</dd>
          </dl>
